title: Mayday.Air.Crash.Investigations.S09.E01.Panic.on.the.Runway.DVD.
description:
Panic on the Runway



Aired on 03/01/2010, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 22 August 1985, an engine of British Airtours Flight 28M, a Boeing 737-200, fails during takeoff, puncturing a hole in the wing fuel tank and starting a fire. The crew successfully abandon the takeoff and stop the aircraft on the runway, but the fire spreads to the cabin; 55 people die before they can evacuate.
